casebody.data:
Tim et al., Respondents, v. Spiegelberg, Appellant. {Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. March 13, 1891.) Appeal from seventh district court.

Argued before Daly, C. J„ and Bisohoff and Pryor, JJ.

Brooke & Brooke, for appellant. D. Tim, for respondents.

*959No opinion. Judgment reversed, and a new trial ordered upon the condition that the appellant within 10 days pay costs of former trial, and appeal. Otherwise judgment affirmed, with costs.
